-2016年間就跟 TVB 小花孫慧雪 (阿雪) 拍過拖，到2016-2018年間就換上 HKTV 小花劉依靜 (Ruby)，最近又換上2010年香港小姐冠軍陳欣庭 (Toby)&hellip; 三個女朋友都曾經坐過他那部溝女戰車。<br />\n<a href=\"http://circle01.life/view1/2861/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcircle01.life%2Fview1%2F2861%2F&d=98Zz%2Fi4ZD3yOQwlUZy72BTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0cee3432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://circle01.life/view1/2861/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屋企開廠 , 咁叫白手興家 ?"},{"pid":"71f20366b8f4e2ccd5ba31f1464f9becedc22628","tid":833264,"uid":46013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛 條女好樣衰 有錢點解唔食好d"},{"pid":"8ffdd80eb0ed2f254c2ddd107b3352a6eb96b40f","tid":833264,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498796cc5b301c3074fdb37ca7c65ebf8c88152d","tid":833264,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b12bac83a286fe86235487fca967bd35463f00f4","tid":833264,"uid":26770,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"之前與有米大狀唐偉倫相戀，後來便與現任男友彩豐行老闆楊振源相戀<br />\n根本所謂相戀係CAREER PATH"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"陳庭欣公屋妹出身  機心重好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"wiki寫佢英國留學唔係有錢都唔會窮"},{"pid":"52e729fedaef0183e9c7b23a5eff6327ba1109dc","tid":833264,"uid":152598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"爛面<br />\n但sell護膚產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e7cb5513eaa7fa574c891a2781db7968449555","tid":833264,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"有無人教佢隻鸚鵡講臭雞臭雞<br />\n陳庭佳一番屋企就臭雞臭雞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20150909/s00009/1441798292261SF_E6210A83805C023013C78783C28FE6D0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20150909%2Fs00009%2F1441798292261SF_E6210A83805C02301